v class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Life Insurance<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-67b95cf elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"67b95cf\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\">Plan ahead and secure your loved ones\u2019 future with our life insurance solutions. We offer education and self-development plans that provide financial security in the event of unforeseen circumstances. These include term life, whole life, and endowment plans, ensuring long-term protection and peace of mind.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-867ef3f elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"867ef3f\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-587f774\" data-id=\"587f774\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-78bcf14 elementor-widget elementor-widget-gva_icon_box_group\" data-id=\"78bcf14\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"gva_icon_box_group.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"gva-element-gva_icon_box_group gva-element\">\r\n<div class=\"gsc-icon-box-group layout-carousel swiper-slider-wrapper \">\r\n   <div class=\"swiper-content-inner\">\r\n      <div class=\"init-carousel-swiper swiper\" data-carousel=\"{&quot;items&quot;:3,&quot;items_lg&quot;:3,&quot;items_md&quot;:3,&quot;items_sm&quot;:2,&quot;items_xs&quot;:2,&quot;items_xx&quot;:2,&quot;effect&quot;:&quot;slide&quot;,&quot;space_between&quot;:30,&quot;loop&quot;:1,&quot;speed&quot;:600,&quot;autoplay&quot;:1,&quot;autoplay_delay&quot;:4500,&quot;autoplay_hover&quot;:1,&quot;navigation&quot;:1,&quot;pagination&quot;:0,&quot;dynamic_bullets&quot;:0,&quot;pagination_type&quot;:&quot;bullets&quot;}\">\r\n         <div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\r\n            <div class=\"swiper-slide\">\r\n<div class=\"icon-box-item elementor-repeater-item-d833a49\">\r\n\t\t\r\n\t\t<div class=\"iconbox-two__single\"><div class=\"iconbox-two__content\"><div class=\"iconbox-two__icon\"><i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\" las la-graduation-cap\"><\/i><\/div><div class=\"iconbox-two__content-inner\"><h3 class=\"iconbox-two__title\">Education Plan<\/h3><div class=\"iconbox-two__desc\">A savings and protection plan that ensures your child\u2019s education is secure. It provides lump sum payouts at key school stages and financial support in case of the policyholder\u2019s passing.<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"swiper-slide\">\r\n<div class=\"icon-box-item elementor-repeater-item-b50c52e\">\r\n\t\t\r\n\t\t<div class=\"iconbox-two__single\"><div class=\"iconbox-two__content\"><div class=\"iconbox-two__icon\"><i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\" las la-lock\"><\/i><\/div><div class=\"iconbox-two__content-inner\"><h3 class=\"iconbox-two__title\">Whole Life Insurance<\/h3><div class=\"iconbox-two__desc\">2. A lifelong cover that guarantees a payout to your loved ones when you pass away. It also builds cash value over time, which you can borrow against if needed.\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"swiper-slide\">\r\n<div class=\"icon-box-item elementor-repeater-item-2c50c28\">\r\n\t\t\r\n\t\t<div class=\"iconbox-two__single\"><div class=\"iconbox-two__content\"><div class=\"iconbox-two__icon\"><i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"far fa-calendar-alt\"><\/i><\/div><div class=\"iconbox-two__content-inner\"><h3 class=\"iconbox-two__title\">Term Insurance<\/h3><div class=\"iconbox-two__desc\"> A cost-effective plan that provides financial protection for a fixed period (e.g., 10, 20, or 30 years). If the policyholder passes away within the term, the beneficiaries receive a payout. However, it does not accumulate savings.<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"swiper-slide\">\r\n<div class=\"icon-box-item elementor-repeater-item-c492c79\">\r\n\t\t\r\n\t\t<div class=\"iconbox-two__single\"><div class=\"iconbox-two__content\"><div class=\"iconbox-two__icon\"><i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\" la la-gear\"><\/i><\/div><div class=\"iconbox-two__content-inner\"><h3 class=\"iconbox-two__title\">Endowment Plan<\/h3><div class=\"iconbox-two__desc\">A combination of savings and life cover. It ensures you receive a lump sum payout at the end of the policy term or provides financial support to your beneficiaries if you pass away before maturity. Ideal for future financial goals like education, homeownership, or retirement.<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"swiper-slide\">\r\n<div class=\"icon-box-item elementor-repeater-item-fb846dd\">\r\n\t\t\r\n\t\t<div class=\"iconbox-two__single\"><div class=\"iconbox-two__content\"><div class=\"iconbox-two__icon\"><i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\" micon__group\"><\/i><\/div><div class=\"iconbox-two__content-inner\"><h3 class=\"iconbox-two__title\">Basic Group Life Cover<\/h3><div class=\"iconbox-two__desc\">Provides a lump sum payout to the dependents of a deceased member, typically based on a multiple of their annual salary.<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"swiper-slide\">\r\n<div class=\"icon-box-item elementor-repeater-item-8376450\">\r\n\t\t\r\n\t\t<div class=\"iconbox-two__single\"><div class=\"iconbox-two__content\"><div class=\"iconbox-two__icon\"><i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fas fa-book-dead\"><\/i><\/div><div class=\"iconbox-two__content-inner\"><h3 class=\"iconbox-two__title\">Group Funeral (Last Expense) Cover<\/h3><div class=\"iconbox-two__desc\">Ensures employees are covered against workplace injuries, disabilities, and occupational diseases, providing compliance with labor laws and financial security.<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"swiper-slide\">\r\n<div class=\"icon-box-item elementor-repeater-item-3282662\">\r\n\t\t\r\n\t\t<div class=\"iconbox-two__single\"><div class=\"iconbox-two__content\"><div class=\"iconbox-two__icon\"><i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\" micon__insurance1\"><\/i><\/div><div class=\"iconbox-two__content-inner\"><h3 class=\"iconbox-two__title\">Group Credit Life Insurance<\/h3><div class=\"iconbox-two__desc\">3. Protects financial institutions by settling outstanding loans if a borrower (group member) passes away.\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"swiper-slide\">\r\n<div class=\"icon-box-item elementor-repeater-item-339605b\">\r\n\t\t\r\n\t\t<div class=\"iconbox-two__single\"><div class=\"iconbox-two__content\"><div class=\"iconbox-two__icon\"><i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\" micon__home-insurance\"><\/i><\/div><div class=\"iconbox-two__content-inner\"><h3 class=\"iconbox-two__title\">Group Mortgage Protection Cover<\/h3><div class=\"iconbox-two__desc\">4. Ensures that outstanding mortgage loans are paid off in case of the policyholder\u2019s death, preventing repossession of property.\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"swiper-slide\">\r\n<div class=\"icon-box-item elementor-repeater-item-1404be4\">\r\n\t\t\r\n\t\t<div class=\"iconbox-two__single\"><div class=\"iconbox-two__content\"><div class=\"iconbox-two__icon\"><i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\" las la-user-injured\"><\/i><\/div><div class=\"iconbox-two__content-inner\"><h3 class=\"iconbox-two__title\">Group Personal Accident (GPA) Cover<\/h3><div class=\"iconbox-two__desc\">Provides compensatio